import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import {FiMessageSquare, FiPlus, FiSearch, FiEdit2} from 'react-icons/fi'; import './dashboard.css'; import Title from '../../components/Title'; import Header from '../../components/Header'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { AuthContext } from '../../contexts/auth'; import firebase from '../../services/firebaseConnection'; export default function Dashboard(){ //criando constante que acessa os chamados pala data de criação const listRef = firebase.firestore().collection('chamados').orderBy('created', 'desc'); const [chamados, setChamados] = useState([]); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [more, setMore] = useState(false); const [isEmpaty, setIsEmapty] = useState(false); useEffect(() => { loadChamados(); }, []) async function loadChamados(){ await listRef.limit(5) .get() .then(()=>{}) .catch((error)=>{ console.log('Deu algum erro: ', error); setMore(false); }) setLoading(false); } return(
